Instruction for installation Platypus on Glassfish Server using Administration Console.
---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

1. Create JDBC pool for database: Resources -> JDBC Connection Pools -> New. Provide url, user, schema and password properties.  

2. Add JDBC Resource for the JDBC pool, set the resource pool name to JDBC pool name from step 1: Resources -> : JDBC Resources - > New

3. Provide schema, user, password, dialect and appElement (optional, for default application element id) properties as context parameters.
